l": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/b/f/bf2e3a8a-b386-474d-b8e9-4c2d56a2b742.jpg?1782722370", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/leg/33/remove-enchantments?utm_source=api", "local": "img/enchant/fa879d99-3d2b-4a9a-a17f-d5ac109f8f44.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Knight of New Benalia", "set": "DOM", "html": "The mage-smiths of New Benalia have perfected the art of blending fine steel and <mark>enchanted</mark> glass into weapons that are both beautiful and deadly. Only elite knights are entrusted with these martial works of art.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/8/88c50c4b-a2c8-4cdc-a171-aa3ff9ef107f.jpg?1782710180"}, {"card": "Aven Gagglemaster", "set": "M21", "html": "An aven&#x27;s gear is <mark>enchanted</mark> to avoid weighing them down during aerial maneuvers.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/5/c5b57247-81cc-44ec-b5a9-0702111a98a8.jpg?1782707008"}, {"card": "Blessed Light", "set": "DOM", "html": "<mark>Enchanted</mark> by mage-smiths and blessed by priests, Benalish windows let in light and cast out darkness.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/4/c/4cf3eb65-0f52-49c1-8243-14ce05de9f3b.jpg?1782710189"}, {"card": "Village Elder", "set": "MIR", "html": "&quot;<mark>Enchant</mark> me with your tale-telling. Tell about Tree, Grass, River, and Wind. / Tell why Truth must fight with Falsehood, and why Truth will always win.&quot;\n—&quot;Love Song of Night and Day&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/5/253a1d97-ec45-41c9-ba81-bbb6ab584b2b.jpg?1782721377"}, {"card": "Teferi's Sentinel", "set": "DOM", "html": "&quot;Long ago, I <mark>enchanted</mark> an army of statues to guard Zhalfir. My homeland is gone, but its protectors remain.&quot;\n—Teferi", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/5/058304f4-f08a-4b3a-ae74-c06f4968c99a.jpg?1782710034"}, {"card": "Hammerheim", "set": "ME3", "html": "&quot;&#x27;Tis distance lends <mark>enchantment</mark> to the view,/ And robes the mountain in its azure hue.&quot;\n—Thomas Campbell, &quot;Pleasures of Hope&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/7/773acde9-504c-4065-95e0-f96428f05a7d.jpg?1782753297"}, {"card": "Shield of the Realm", "set": "DOM", "html": "Benalish glazeplate is stained with salts from the Rift Era and <mark>enchanted</mark> to deflect blows.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/2/7207edf8-8534-4982-969f-df97febcb9fc.jpg?1782710059"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Sensory Deprivation", "set": "M14", "html": "<mark>Enchant</mark> creature\n<mark>Enchanted</mark> creature gets -3/-0."}, {"card": "Waterknot", "set": "JMP", "html": "<mark>Enchant</mark> creature\nWhen this Aura enters, tap <mark>enchanted</mark> creature.\n<mark>Enchanted</mark> creature doesn&#x27;t untap during its controller&#x27;s untap step."}, {"card": "Lattice Library", "set": "SOC", "html": "This <mark>enchantment</mark> enters with X study counters on it."}, {"card": "Aura Graft", "set": "10E", "html": "Gain control of target Aura that&#x27;s attached to a permanent. Attach it to another permanent it can <mark>enchant</mark>."}, {"card": "Kindred Discovery", "set": "MSC", "html": "As this <mark>enchantment</mark> enters, choose a creature type.\nWhenever a creature you control of the chosen type enters or attacks, draw a card."}, {"card": "Strength of Unity", "set": "INV", "html": "<mark>Enchant</mark> creature\nDomain — <mark>Enchanted</mark> creature gets +1/+1 for each basic land type among lands you control."}, {"card": "One with the Kami", "set": "NEC", "html": "<mark>Enchant</mark> creature you control"}, {"card": "Pharika's Mender", "set": "CN2", "html": "When this creature enters, you may return target creature or <mark>enchantment</mark> card from your graveyard to your hand."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/0/7050735c-b232-47a6-a342-01795bfd0d46.jpg?1782713954", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/7/0/7050735c-b232-47a6-a342-01795bfd0d46.jpg?1782713954", "card": "Sensory Deprivation"}}